# textdomain: mcl_redstone
Transmits redstone power, powers mechanisms=Harrigorri seinalea transmititzen du, mekanismoak bultzatzen ditu
Redstone is a versatile conductive mineral which transmits redstone power. It can be placed on the ground as a trail.=Harrigorri mineral eroale moldakorra da, harrigorri energia transmititzen duena. Lurrean bidezidor bat bezala jar daiteke.
A redstone trail can be in two states: Powered or not powered. A powered redstone trail will power (and thus activate) adjacent redstone components.=Harrigorri bidezidor bat bi egoeratan egon daiteke: elikatuta edo elikatu gabe. Harrigorri arrasto elikatu batek ondoko harrigorri osagaiak elikatuko (eta, beraz, aktibatuko) ditu.
Redstone power can be received from various redstone components, such as a block of redstone or a button. Redstone power is used to activate numerous mechanisms, such as redstone lamps or pistons.=Harrigorri-ren boterea hainbat redstone-osagaitatik jaso daiteke, hala nola harrigorri-bloke batetik edo botoi batetik. Harrigorriren boterea mekanismo ugari aktibatzeko erabiltzen da, hala nola harrigorri lanparak edo pistoiak.
Place redstone on the ground to build a redstone trail. The trails will connect to each other automatically and it can also go over hills.=Jarri harrigorri lurrean harrigorri bidexka bat eraikitzeko. Bidezidorrak automatikoki lotuko dira elkarren artean, eta muinoetatik ere igaro daitezke.
Read the help entries on the other redstone components to learn how redstone components interact.=Irakurri laguntza sarrerak beste harrigorri osagaiak nola elkarrekintzan ikasteko.
Redstone Dust=Harrigorri Hautsa
